<Legal title="Privacy Policy — Remotely Human" heading="Privacy Policy">
  <h2><span>1.</span>Who We Are</h2>
  <p>
    We are <strong>Remotely Human LLC</strong> (“we”, “us”, “our”), and this is
    our privacy policy. It applies to all tools, automations, services, and
    software hosted under remotelyhuman.com and any subdomains (e.g.,
    workflows.remotelyhuman.com).
  </p>

  <h2><span>2.</span>What We Collect</h2>
  <p>Depending on what you use, we may collect:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Name and email address</li>
    <li>Google account data (e.g., Gmail access if you connect through OAuth)</li>
    <li>Emails and messages (only if your automation accesses them)</li>
    <li>Workflow data you provide or process through our tools</li>
    <li>Log data (IP address, browser type, usage info)</li>
  </ul>

  <h2><span>3.</span>How We Use Your Data</h2>
  <p>We use your data to:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Authenticate you through third-party providers like Google</li>
    <li>Provide and improve automation tools and services</li>
    <li>Operate workflows you’ve designed or requested</li>
    <li>Communicate with you if needed</li>
    <li>Comply with laws and protect your data</li>
  </ul>
  <p>
    <strong>We do not sell your data to third parties.</strong> We only access
    the data you authorize (e.g. Gmail) for the automation features you choose.
  </p>

  <h2><span>4.</span>Third-Party Services</h2>
  <p>We may connect with services like:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Gmail / Google APIs</li>
    <li>Airtable, Slack, Telegram, Notion, and others</li>
  </ul>
  <p>
    These connections only happen with your permission and are limited to
    scopes you explicitly approve (e.g. send email, read inbox).
  </p>

  <h2><span>5.</span>Data Retention</h2>
  <p>We store workflow data and logs only as long as needed to:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Deliver the service</li>
    <li>Debug issues</li>
    <li>Comply with legal or security requirements</li>
  </ul>
  <p>You can delete your data at any time by contacting us.</p>

  <h2><span>6.</span>Your Rights</h2>
  <p>You can:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Request a copy of your data</li>
    <li>Ask us to delete your data</li>
    <li>Revoke OAuth access at any time from your Google Account</li>
  </ul>
  <p class="contact-block">
    To request anything, just contact us at:<br />
    📧 <a href="mailto:web@remotelyhuman.com">web@remotelyhuman.com</a>
  </p>

  <h2><span>7.</span>Security</h2>
  <p>
    We use modern, encrypted infrastructure. Credentials and API tokens are
    stored securely. We follow least-privilege access principles and don’t read
    your data unless required for support or debugging (and only with
    permission).
  </p>

  <h2><span>8.</span>Changes to This Policy</h2>
  <p>
    We may update this privacy policy at any time. When we do, we’ll update the
    “Last Updated” date at the top.
  </p>

  <h2><span>9.</span>Contact</h2>
  <p class="contact-block">
    Questions? Contact us at:<br />
    📧 <a href="mailto:web@remotelyhuman.com">web@remotelyhuman.com</a><br />
    📍 30 North Gould, Sheridan WY, 82801
  </p>
</Legal>
